snippet.title: Snakebird Primer announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Snakebird Primer is a more forgiving puzzle game based on the extremely difficult Snakebird.
Set to challenge puzzlers of all ages as well as prime you for the challenges in the original Snakebird.

Worm your way though 72 levels featuring easy to learn mechanics and puzzling puzzles.
